description:
Oral- B Pro-Health Advanced Toothpaste Whitening Mint for healthy gums and strong teeth. Strengthens inside protects outside* (*Strengthens enamel and protects the outside from acids in everyday food)

Oral-B Pro-Health Complete Defence System Whitening is a complete defence system for your mouth with antibacterial fighters, enamel builders and pH shield. It provides 24 hour protection from harmful plaque bacteria* It has whitening ingredients for a natural white smile. *with twice daily brushing

Antibacterial Fighters neutralise harmful plaque bacteria and inhibit their regrowth

Enamel Builders help restore weakened enamel on a daily basis

pH Shield protects teeth enamel from acid erosion due to daily foods

Fights plaque bacteria, prevents cavities, freshens breath, prevents tartar, whitens teeth by removing surface stains, promotes gum health and protects enamel.

For a complete oral care regimen, also use an Oral-B toothbrush, floss and rinse. Visit your dentist regularly.
name: Oral-b Pro Health Toothpaste Advanced Whitening 110G
